    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M-Division engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS. The powertrain is mated to a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering torque through a Variable M Differential Lock. This vehicle is mechanically impeccable; the common E46 failure points have been proactively addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, and rod bearing replacement with high-performance shells. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping and lateral stiffness, ensuring the chassis remains neutral under high-G loads. Finished in original paint with an interior devoid of bolster wear or pixel degradation, this vehicle offers a turn-key experience for the serious collector or driving enthusiast who demands mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
