      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true showroom-quality vehicle. Finished in its original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, there isn't a single stone chip, swirl mark, or door ding to be found. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery shows zero bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since day one. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage and has a comprehensive service history documented from the date of purchase. All electronics, switches, and performance features function exactly as they did the day it left the dealership. We have recently performed a preventative fluid flush and a 150-point inspection to ensure it is turn-key ready for its next owner. This sale includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker.",
